description:
Tanner and Cory both like to have a good time outdoors and just goof off, so what’s a great way to put all that energy to use? A water balloon fight! How does that old saying go again? “Boys will be boys.” That is definitely appropriate for these two studs playing around and getting each other wet.

When it came to getting down to business, they couldn’t keep their hands off each other! Cory really went all out on Tanner’s ass. 

“I’m just letting him do his thing!” Tanner definitely enjoyed the ride.

It was an extra treat to see Cory shoot his load into Tanner and watch it drip out of his ass!
title: Tanner & Cory: Bareback
